nodes.title: Final prompt preview
widgets_values: The video shows a young woman with pale skin and long, wavy silver hair, wearing a white, off-the-shoulder dress with long sleeves. She has a serious expression and is standing against a plain, light pink background. The dress has a low neckline and falls just above her knees. She is wearing silver earrings. The video has a soft, dreamy quality with a minimalist aesthetic. The woman is positioned in the center of the frame, facing the camera. The woman dance.
